quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,Ife tavumbulutsa mutu uwu ndipo taupanga kukhala wokakamiza ndipo ndi mwa iwo mmene tavumbulutsa chivumbulutsochoonekakutiinumukhozakuchenjezedwa
  24,2,"Munthu wamkazi wosakwatiwa akachita chigololo ndi munthu wamwamuna wosakwatira, mukwapule aliyense wa iwo zikoti zana limodzi ndipo musalole kuti chifundo chikulepheretseni kumvera lamulo la Mulungu ngati inu mumakhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi tsiku lomaliza. Ndipo onetsetsani kuti chilango chawo chachitidwa umboni ndi anthu ambiri okhulupirira"
  24,3,Mwamuna wachigololo asakwatire wina koma mkazi wachigololo kapena mkazi wopembedza mafano. Mkazi wachigololo asakwatiwe ndi wina koma mwamuna wachigololo kapena wopembedza mafano. Anthu okhulupirira moona saloledwa maukwati otere
  24,4,"Iwo amene amanamizira akazi odzisunga kuti achita chigololo ndipo sangathe kutulutsa mboni zinayi, akwapulidwe zikoti makumi asanu ndi atatu. Mukane umboni wawo mpaka kalekale. Anthu otere ndi oononga"
  24,5,"Kupatulaokhawoamene, patapitanthawi, alapandikusiya makhalidwe awo onyansa. Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha"
  24,6,"Ndipo ngati mwamuna akuti mkazi wake wachita chigololo koma alibe mboni kupatula iye mwini, iye alumbire kanayi dzina la Mulungu kuti zimene ali kunena ndi zoona"
  24,7,Ndipo kachisanu anene kuti matemberero a Mulungu akhale pa iye mwamunayo ngati ali kunama
  24,8,"Koma ngati mkazi wake alumbira kanayi, potchula dzina la Mulungu, kutsutsa kuti zimene ali kunena mwamuna wake ndi zabodza, sadzalandira chilango"
  24,9,Ndipo kachisanu ayenera kunena kuti mkwiyo wa Mulungu ukhale pa iye mkaziyo ngati ali kunama
  24,10,Pakadapanda chisoni ndi chisomo cha Mulungu mukadaonongeka. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi waluntha
  24,11,"Iwo amene adapeka nkhani yabodzayi, adali gulu la anthu anu omwe. Usaganize kuti ndi masoka koma ndi zabwino kwa inu. Aliyense adzalangidwa molingana ndi tchimo lake. Akakhala iye amene amaikulitsa nkhaniyi, chilango chake chidzakhala chowawa kwambiri"
  24,12,"Pamenemudamvankhaniyi, bwanjianthuokhulupirira, amuna ndi akazi, sadafune kuganizira zabwino za anthu awo ndi kunena kuti, “Ili ndi bodza loonekera poyera?”"
  24,13,Kodi ndi chifukwa chiyani iwo sadabweretse mboni zinayi? Ngati iwo adalephera kutulutsa mboni ndiye kuti iwo anali kunama pamaso pa Mulungu
  24,14,"Kukadakhala kuti Mulungu sadaonetse chisomo ndi chifundo chake pa inu, m’moyo uno ndiponso m’moyo umene uli nkudza, mukadalangidwa kwambiri chifukwa cha zimene mwakhala mukuchita"
  24,15,"Pamene inu munali kunena ndi malirime anu ndiponso kuyankhula ndi pakamwa panu zinthu zimene simunali kuzidziwa, inu munali kuganiza kuti izi zidali zopepuka koma pamaso pa Mulungu zinali zazikulu"
  24,16,"Pamene mudazimva, bwanji inu simudanene kuti, “Si koyenera kuti ife tikambe izi ayi. Mulungu ayeretsedwe! Kumeneku ndiko kunama kwenikweni.”"
  24,17,Mulungu ali kukuchenjezani kuti musadzachitenso izi ngati inu ndinu anthu okhulupirira m’choonadi
  24,18,Mulungu ali kukufotokozerani momveka chivumbulutso chake. Iye ndi wanzeru ndipo amadziwa zonse
  24,19,"Iwo amene amasangalala kuti nkhani zoipa zokhudza anthu okhulupirira zifalikire, adzalangidwa kwambiri m’moyo umene uli nkudza. Mulungu ali kudziwa zonse pamene inu simudziwa"
  24,20,"Pakadakhala popanda chisomo cha Mulungu kwa inu, nonse mukanaonongedwa. Ndithudi Mulungu ndi wabwino ndiponso wachisoni"